data.description: BACK ON THE MARKET!!! BUYER COULD NOT PERFORM. Welcome to this great single family home located in the desirable North Moreno Valley area.  As you enter  you're greeted by an elegant staircase and a large living room with a warm fireplace which adds character to the home. Provides cozy focal point for gatherings and seamlessly connects to the dining area and creating the perfect environment for everyday living. The kitchen features stainless steel appliances window over the sink that offers a nice view of the backyard. A sliding door from the dining area leads out to the patio space, where you can enjoy outdoor dining and leisure in your private backyard. Upstairs, the primary beautiful suite with a door leading to a balcony, a large wall closet, and an ensuite bathroom featuring a dual sink  and an oversized tub/shower combo. Two secondary bedrooms, located at the opposite side.  Convenient second full bathroom, ensuring ample space for everyone. Natural light pours in from every angle, enhancing the welcoming ambiance of this home. Convenience is key with this home's prime location and peaceful neighborhood providing easy access to the 60, 215 and 91 freeways, as well as local markets, shopping, and a variety of dining options. This home seamlessly combines style, comfort, and accessibility. Don't miss the opportunity to make it yours. Schedule your viewing today.
